reviewText: I couldn't ask for better as both my son, my husband and I enjoy each one of these movies. They all play perfectly. 4 Star only because the box is week and flimsy but most things are built that way now days!
These are three very good movies.  I went out on a limb on Eragon, but the kids ended up liking it as much as the other two.  I think that this is an awesome set for family night...
